Question: In at least one image there are four women in bikinis.

Reference Answer: False

Left image URL: https://firstin.files.wordpress.com/2008/11/eagles-girls.jpg?w=450

Right image URL: https://i.pinimg.com/originals/14/b7/31/14b7319fc8ec88817dda3558fe5f9557.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many women are in bikinis in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many women are in bikinis in the image?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} >= 4 or {ANSWER1} >= 4')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
